---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="Cello | Connect, protect and observe what keeps your business running"
	description="Cello brings together accountable business connectivity, service visibility and practical digital resilience for organisations that depend on reliable networks."
>
	<section class="hero">
		<div class="hero-inner">
			<div class="hero-copy">
				<p class="eyebrow">Business-only networks, expanded for resilience</p>
				<h1>Connect, protect and observe what keeps your business running.</h1>
				<p class="lead">
					Cello is New Zealand's largest specialist enterprise network provider:
					business-only connectivity you can depend on. That foundation can now
					extend into practical visibility, security and automation so enterprise
					and regulated teams can act on risk before it becomes disruption.
				</p>
				<div class="actions">
					<a class="button" href="/contact">Talk to our team</a>
					<a class="button secondary" href="/solutions/smartwan">Explore SmartWAN</a>
				</div>
				<div class="trust-strip" aria-label="Trusted sectors">
					<span>Banking</span>
					<span>Government</span>
					<span>Utilities</span>
					<span>Infrastructure</span>
					<span>Enterprise IT</span>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section" id="industries">
		<div class="section-header">
			<div>
				<p class="eyebrow">The Cello difference</p>
				<h2>Networks still come first.</h2>
			</div>
			<p class="lead">
				Cello's strength remains service excellence: one accountable team, a
				business-only backbone and local engineers who stay with the outcome.
			</p>
		</div>
		<div class="metric-grid">
			<div class="tile">
				<strong>2,000+ km</strong>
				<p>Business-dedicated network infrastructure across New Zealand.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="tile">
				<strong>130+</strong>
				<p>Network specialists focused on enterprise environments.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="tile">
				<strong>24/7</strong>
				<p>Local NOC monitoring and response for critical operations.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="tile">
				<strong>100%</strong>
				<p>New Zealand-owned, with decisions made close to customers.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section">
		<div class="split">
			<div class="copy">
				<p class="eyebrow">Business network services</p>
				<h2>From reliable networks to clearer operating confidence.</h2>
				<p>
					Cello starts with trusted connectivity and can extend that service
					commitment into clearer visibility, assurance and support around the
					systems customers depend on.
				</p>
				<ul>
					<li>Connect sites, users and cloud services through accountable design.</li>
					<li>Protect the environments that carry business-critical activity.</li>
					<li>Observe signals early enough to make better decisions under pressure.</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
			<div class="ink-panel">
				<p class="eyebrow">Customer promise</p>
				<p class="quote">
					Cello brings connectivity, visibility and assurance together through
					one accountable service relationship.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section topology" id="resilience">
		<div class="section-header">
			<div>
				<p class="eyebrow">Digital resilience</p>
				<h2>See earlier. Respond faster. Prove control.</h2>
			</div>
			<p class="lead">
				Cello keeps resilience practical: reliable networks, clear service
				visibility and responsive support without unnecessary complexity.
			</p>
		</div>
		<div class="capability-grid">
			<div class="tile">
				<h3>Observability</h3>
				<p>Unify telemetry so teams see how systems behave before pressure escalates.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="tile">
				<h3>Security</h3>
				<p>Surface risk earlier with signals that are complete, reliable and useful.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="tile">
				<h3>Automation</h3>
				<p>Reduce manual intervention and shorten response when something changes.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="tile">
				<h3>Assurance</h3>
				<p>Give leaders evidence for resilience, not just statements of intent.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section">
		<div class="section-header">
			<div>
				<p class="eyebrow">How we work</p>
				<h2>Structured where it counts.</h2>
			</div>
			<p class="lead">
				The customer experience stays Cello: practical, accountable and clear from
				first workshop through daily operations.
			</p>
		</div>
		<div class="process">
			<div class="process-item">
				<h3>Assess</h3>
				<p>Map sites, risk, operational pressure and the systems that matter most.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="process-item">
				<h3>Design</h3>
				<p>Shape the right network and resilience pattern for the environment.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="process-item">
				<h3>Deliver</h3>
				<p>Implement carefully, with clear cutovers and one accountable team.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="process-item">
				<h3>Run</h3>
				<p>Monitor, improve and report so confidence strengthens over time.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section" id="proof">
		<div class="proof-grid">
			<div class="tile">
				<p class="eyebrow">Proven Cello service</p>
				<p class="quote">
					"Developing and implementing the network solution was seamless and
					offered us new and improved security."
				</p>
				<p>Brian Northern, Group CIO, Fulton Hogan</p>
			</div>
			<div class="tile">
				<p class="eyebrow">What customers can expect</p>
				<h3>A broader customer promise built on Cello's network service excellence.</h3>
				<p>
					Cello keeps the trusted network message in front while showing how
					service visibility and assurance strengthen the customer experience.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section">
		<div class="section-header">
			<div>
				<p class="eyebrow">Explore Cello services</p>
				<h2>Three ways to work with Cello.</h2>
			</div>
			<p class="lead">
				Choose the path that matches your needs, from core connectivity to
				service visibility and practical resilience support.
			</p>
		</div>
		<div class="solution-grid">
			<a class="tile" href="/solutions/smartwan">
				<h3>SmartWAN</h3>
				<p>Business-only wide-area networking with one team owning the outcome.</p>
			</a>
			<a class="tile" href="/digital-resilience">
				<h3>Digital resilience</h3>
				<p>Visibility, security, automation and evidence for the systems that matter.</p>
			</a>
			<a class="tile" href="/contact">
				<h3>Talk to our team</h3>
				<p>A simple path to start a conversation with the Cello team.</p>
			</a>
			<div class="tile">
				<h3>Regulated enterprise</h3>
				<p>Language tuned for teams where uptime, assurance and accountability matter.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="cta">
		<div>
			<p class="eyebrow">Next step</p>
			<h2>Talk to Cello about stronger business connectivity.</h2>
			<p>
				Connect with our team to discuss network services, visibility and
				practical resilience options for your organisation.
			</p>
		</div>
		<a class="button" href="/contact">Contact Cello</a>
	</section>
</Layout>
